hopobject.body: Could you transfer $1000 from my current account to my deposit account? al abeer medical group madinah You'd think Microsoft would have noticed this phenomenon and reacted accordingly. If Microsoft had put 32 to 64GB of memory in these Windows RT tablets and blew out the six million units rotting in the warehouse at $150 each, it would have reaped $900 million in sales. That sum would have negated the $900 million write-down and—boom!—Microsoft is now gold. The stock would have continued to skyrocket. But no.
